---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="relative py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="About"
      title="Operator instincts. Builder reps."
    />
    <div class="reveal mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-4xl gap-8 text-lg text-mist-300 md:grid-cols-2">
      <p>
        I have spent ten years scaling identity, trust, and ML systems at Airbnb and Twitter. Today I lead 19 engineers across Identity Platform, Defense, and Business Verification. My systems protect millions of users every day and delivered $23.9M in annualized impact last year.
      </p>
      <p>
        In parallel I have been shipping AI-native products solo: Loadout (a Claude Code OS guide), Verso (an iOS reading agent), and Glassbox AI (visual QA tooling). Now looking for the right zero-to-one team where operator discipline and founder velocity matter equally.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
